data.title: US military defied Trump ban, used Anthropic in Iran strike: WSJUS military used Anthropic's Claude AI for intel analysis in Iran strike despite Trump ban.

This highlights the significance of Anthropic's technology in military operations, emphasizing its crucial role in decision-making processes. The incident underscores the complexities surrounding the use of AI in defense and national security strategies, indicating a shift towards advanced technological solutions in modern warfare.
